      "role": "user",
      "content": "thx. u mentioned \"promised economic expansion\"—it feels like a lot of the academic consensus is leaning towards the critics on this one though. like, don't most recent studies suggest that these kinds of corporate cuts don't actually trickledown like they claim? would u say the 'proponent' side is actually backed by much evidence or is it more of a theoretical hope?",
